platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 投入回合制的中古戰爭冒險

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The same thought popped into our head again and again while playing Banner Saga 2: We’re gonna remember this game. The gripping story. The thrilling turn-based battles. The heroes we lost in our struggle against the Dredge. Epic in every way, it’s a beautiful and heart-rending adventure.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: A stunning story with epic battles.
Une histoire incroyable ponctuée d'affrontements épiques.
